```plantuml
@startuml IBM_IBM-Spectrum-Scale-Security-Posture

actor User
participant "cronjob.py" as Cronjob
participant "fetch_security_posture_and_upload_to_ES.sh" as FetchScript
participant "collector/security_posture.py" as Collector
participant "split_json_for_kibana.py" as Splitter
participant "Elasticsearch"
participant "Kibana"

User -> Cronjob: Schedule Job
Cronjob -> FetchScript: Trigger Data Collection
FetchScript -> Collector: Execute Security Data Collection
Collector -> SpectrumScaleCluster: Gather Security Data
SpectrumScaleCluster -> Collector: Return Security Data
Collector -> FetchScript: Pass JSON Data

FetchScript -> Splitter: Split JSON Data
Splitter -> FetchScript: Return Split JSON Files
FetchScript -> Elasticsearch: Upload Data via curl
FetchScript -> Elasticsearch: Authenticate (security-posture.conf)

Elasticsearch -> Kibana: Data Available for Visualization
User -> Kibana: Access Dashboard
Kibana -> User: Display Security Posture

@enduml
```